document.full_text: israeli naval commandos on tuesday seized a cargo ship in the mediterranean carrying what prime minister benjamin netanyahu said were iranian-supplied weapons intended for palestinian militants in the gaza strip.
document.title: israel seizes ship with iran arms for gaza-netanyahu
